class PointGNNEncoder(nn.Module):
    def __init__(self, in_dim=3, hidden_dim=64, out_dim=128):
        super().__init__()
        self.conv1 = GCNConv(in_dim, hidden_dim)
        self.conv2 = GCNConv(hidden_dim, hidden_dim)
        self.lin = nn.Linear(hidden_dim, out_dim)

    def forward(self, batch_graph):
        x = F.relu(self.conv1(batch_graph.x, batch_graph.edge_index))
        x = F.relu(self.conv2(x, batch_graph.edge_index))
        x = global_mean_pool(x, batch_graph.batch)
        return self.lin(x)

# 图卷积 GCN Block（ResNet+BN+Dropout+JK）
class DeepGCNEncoder(nn.Module):
    def __init__(self, in_dim=3, hidden_dim=128, out_dim=128, num_layers=6):
        super().__init__()
        assert num_layers >= 2
        self.in_proj = nn.Linear(in_dim, hidden_dim)

        self.convs = nn.ModuleList([GCNConv(hidden_dim, hidden_dim) for _ in range(num_layers)])
        self.bns   = nn.ModuleList([BatchNorm(hidden_dim) for _ in range(num_layers)])
        self.dropout = 0.2
        # Jumping Knowledge 汇聚多层表示（"cat" 或 "max" 都可）
        self.jk = JumpingKnowledge(mode="cat", channels=hidden_dim, num_layers=num_layers)
        self.out = nn.Linear(hidden_dim * num_layers, out_dim)

    def forward(self, batch_graph):
        x, edge_index, batch = batch_graph.x, batch_graph.edge_index, batch_graph.batch
        x = self.in_proj(x)
        xs = []
        for conv, bn in zip(self.convs, self.bns):
            residual = x
            x = conv(x, edge_index)
            x = bn(x)
            x = F.relu(x)
            x = F.dropout(x, p=self.dropout, training=self.training)
            x = x + residual  # pre-activation 残差
            xs.append(x)

        x = self.jk(xs)                      # [∑N, hidden_dim*num_layers]
        x = global_mean_pool(x, batch)       # [B, hidden_dim*num_layers]
        return self.out(x)                   # [B, out_dim]


# 图注意力 Block（多头 GATv2 + 残差）
class GATEncoder(nn.Module):
    def __init__(self, in_dim=3, hidden_dim=64, out_dim=128, heads=4, layers=3, concat_last=True):
        super().__init__()
        self.in_proj = nn.Linear(in_dim, hidden_dim)

        self.layers = nn.ModuleList()
        self.bns    = nn.ModuleList()
        for i in range(layers):
            in_ch  = hidden_dim * heads if i > 0 else hidden_dim
            out_ch = hidden_dim
            self.layers.append(GATv2Conv(in_ch, out_ch, heads=heads, dropout=0.2, concat=True))
            self.bns.append(BatchNorm(out_ch * heads))

        self.dropout = 0.2
        self.concat_last = concat_last
        last_dim = hidden_dim * heads
        self.out = nn.Linear(last_dim, out_dim)

    def forward(self, batch_graph):
        x, edge_index, batch = batch_graph.x, batch_graph.edge_index, batch_graph.batch
        x = self.in_proj(x)
        for conv, bn in zip(self.layers, self.bns):
            residual = x
            x = conv(x, edge_index)   # [∑N, hidden*heads]
            x = bn(x)
            x = F.elu(x)
            x = F.dropout(x, p=self.dropout, training=self.training)
            # 对齐通道后再残差（若维度不同则跳过）
            if residual.shape[-1] == x.shape[-1]:
                x = x + residual
        x = global_mean_pool(x, batch)
        return self.out(x)

# 图 U-Net Block（GraphUNet 主干 + 池化/上采样）
class GraphUNetEncoder(nn.Module):
    def __init__(self, in_dim=3, hidden_dim=64, out_dim=128, depth=4, pool_ratios=0.5, act=F.relu):
        super().__init__()
        # GraphUNet: 输入维度 -> 隐藏维度 -> 输出维度（逐层上下采样）
        self.proj_in  = nn.Linear(in_dim, hidden_dim)
        self.gunet    = GraphUNet(hidden_dim, hidden_dim, hidden_dim, depth=depth, pool_ratios=pool_ratios)
        self.proj_out = nn.Linear(hidden_dim, out_dim)
        self.act = act
        self.dropout = 0.2

    def forward(self, batch_graph):
        x, edge_index, batch = batch_graph.x, batch_graph.edge_index, batch_graph.batch
        x = self.act(self.proj_in(x))
        x = F.dropout(x, p=self.dropout, training=self.training)
        x = self.gunet(x, edge_index)              # 逐点隐藏表示
        x = self.act(x)
        x = global_mean_pool(x, batch)
        x = F.dropout(x, p=self.dropout, training=self.training)
        return self.proj_out(x)


# EGNN Block（E(n) 等变，更新坐标与特征）
class EGNNLayer(nn.Module):
    def __init__(self, x_dim, edge_attr_dim=0, hidden_dim=64):
        super().__init__()
        self.phi_e = nn.Sequential(                 # 边消息 MLP: ϕ_e(h_i, h_j, ||x_i - x_j||^2)
            nn.Linear(2 * x_dim + 1 + edge_attr_dim, hidden_dim),
            nn.SiLU(),
            nn.Linear(hidden_dim, hidden_dim),
            nn.SiLU(),
        )
        self.phi_x = nn.Sequential(                 # 坐标更新系数
            nn.Linear(hidden_dim, 1),
        )
        self.phi_h = nn.Sequential(                 # 节点特征更新 ϕ_h(h_i, Σ m_ij)
            nn.Linear(x_dim + hidden_dim, hidden_dim),
            nn.SiLU(),
            nn.Linear(hidden_dim, x_dim),
        )

    def forward(self, x, pos, edge_index, edge_attr=None):
        i, j = edge_index   # i <- j
        # pairwise
        diff = pos[i] - pos[j]                 # [E, d]
        dist2 = (diff * diff).sum(dim=-1, keepdim=True)  # [E,1]
        m_ij_in = [x[i], x[j], dist2]
        if edge_attr is not None:
            m_ij_in.append(edge_attr)
        m_ij_in = torch.cat(m_ij_in, dim=-1)   # [E, 2*x_dim + 1 + edge_attr_dim]
        m_ij = self.phi_e(m_ij_in)             # [E, hidden]

        # 坐标更新（对称、等变）
        trans = self.phi_x(m_ij) * diff        # [E, d]
        # 聚合到节点 i
        delta_x = torch.zeros_like(pos)
        delta_x.index_add_(0, i, trans)        # sum_j m_ij
        pos = pos + delta_x                    # 更新坐标

        # 节点特征更新
        agg = torch.zeros(x.size(0), m_ij.size(-1), device=x.device)
        agg.index_add_(0, i, m_ij)             # sum_j m_ij
        x = self.phi_h(torch.cat([x, agg], dim=-1))
        return x, pos

class EGNNEncoder(nn.Module):
    def __init__(self, in_dim=1, coord_dim=2, hidden_dim=64, out_dim=128, layers=4):
        """
        in_dim: 节点特征维度（例如相场 phi）
        coord_dim: 坐标维度（2D: x,y 或 3D: x,y,z）
        """
        super().__init__()
        self.x_in = nn.Linear(in_dim, hidden_dim)
        self.layers = nn.ModuleList([EGNNLayer(hidden_dim, edge_attr_dim=0, hidden_dim=hidden_dim) for _ in range(layers)])
        self.x_out = nn.Linear(hidden_dim, out_dim)

    def forward(self, batch_graph):
        x, pos, edge_index, batch = batch_graph.x, batch_graph.pos, batch_graph.edge_index, batch_graph.batch
        x = F.silu(self.x_in(x))                 # 节点初始投影
        for layer in self.layers:
            x, pos = layer(x, pos, edge_index, edge_attr=None)
        x = global_mean_pool(x, batch)           # 仅池化特征（pos 只用于中间更新）
        return self.x_out(x)


# GINConv + TopKPool（表达力强 + 图下采样，适合大点云）
class GINTopKEncoder(nn.Module):
    def __init__(self, in_dim=3, hidden_dim=64, out_dim=128, pool_ratio=0.8, layers=3):
        super().__init__()
        self.proj_in = nn.Linear(in_dim, hidden_dim)

        self.convs = nn.ModuleList()
        self.bns   = nn.ModuleList()
        self.pools = nn.ModuleList()
        for _ in range(layers):
            nn_mlp = nn.Sequential(
                nn.Linear(hidden_dim, hidden_dim),
                nn.ReLU(),
                nn.Linear(hidden_dim, hidden_dim),
            )
            self.convs.append(GINConv(nn_mlp))
            self.bns.append(BatchNorm(hidden_dim))
            self.pools.append(TopKPooling(hidden_dim, ratio=pool_ratio))

        self.dropout = 0.2
        self.out = nn.Linear(hidden_dim, out_dim)

    def forward(self, batch_graph):
        x, edge_index, batch = batch_graph.x, batch_graph.edge_index, batch_graph.batch
        x = F.relu(self.proj_in(x))
        for conv, bn, pool in zip(self.convs, self.bns, self.pools):
            x = F.relu(bn(conv(x, edge_index)))
            x, edge_index, _, batch, _, _ = pool(x, edge_index, None, batch)
            x = F.dropout(x, p=self.dropout, training=self.training)
        x = global_mean_pool(x, batch)
        return self.out(x)

class MLP_Block(nn.Module):
    def __init__(self, input_dim, hidden_channel, output_dim, hidden_size=4):
        super(MLP_Block, self).__init__()
        self.activation = nn.Tanh()
        self.IN = nn.Linear(input_dim, hidden_channel)
        self.hidden_layers = nn.ModuleList([
            nn.Linear(hidden_channel, hidden_channel) for _ in range(hidden_size)
        ])
        self.OUT = nn.Linear(hidden_channel, output_dim)
        self._init_weights()

    def _init_weights(self):
        for m in self.modules():
            if isinstance(m, nn.Linear):
                nn.init.normal_(m.weight, mean=0.0, std=0.1)
                nn.init.constant_(m.bias, 0.0)

    def forward(self, x):
        x = self.activation(self.IN(x))
        for layer in self.hidden_layers:
            x = self.activation(layer(x))
        x = self.OUT(x)
        return x

class Modified_MLP_Block(nn.Module):
    def __init__(self, input_dim, hidden_channel, output_dim, hidden_size=4):
        super(Modified_MLP_Block, self).__init__()
        self.activation = nn.Tanh()
        self.encodeU = nn.Linear(input_dim, hidden_channel)
        self.encodeV = nn.Linear(input_dim, hidden_channel)
        self.In = nn.Linear(input_dim, hidden_channel)

        self.hidden_layers = nn.ModuleList([
            nn.Linear(hidden_channel, hidden_channel) for _ in range(hidden_size)
        ])
        self.out = nn.Linear(hidden_channel, output_dim)
        self._init_weights()

    def _init_weights(self):
        for m in self.modules():
            if isinstance(m, nn.Linear):
                nn.init.normal_(m.weight, mean=0.0, std=0.1)
                nn.init.constant_(m.bias, 0.0)

    def forward(self, x):
        U = self.activation(self.encodeU(x))
        V = self.activation(self.encodeV(x))
        Hidden = self.activation(self.In(x))

        for layer in self.hidden_layers:
            Z = self.activation(layer(Hidden))
            Hidden = (1 - Z) * U + Z * V

        x = self.out(Hidden)
        return x

def pointcloud_to_graph(B_phase, k=8, if_depart=True):
    if if_depart:
        pos = B_phase[:, :2]
        node_features = B_phase[:, 2].unsqueeze(1)
        edge_index = knn_graph(pos, k=k, loop=False)
        row, col = edge_index
        edge_attr = pos[col] - pos[row]

        data = Data(x=node_features, pos=pos, edge_index=edge_index, edge_attr=edge_attr)
    else:
        edge_index = knn_graph(B_phase, k=k, batch=None, loop=False)
        data = Data(x=B_phase, edge_index=edge_index)
    return data

class FourierEmbedding(nn.Module):
    def __init__(self, input_dim, mapping_size=256, scale=10.0):
        super().__init__()
        self.B = nn.Parameter(scale * torch.randn((mapping_size, input_dim)), requires_grad=False)

    def forward(self, x):
        x_proj = 2 * np.pi * x @ self.B.T
        return torch.cat([torch.sin(x_proj), torch.cos(x_proj)], dim=-1)

class FractureNet(nn.Module):
    def __init__(self, point_dim=128, mode = 'norm_GCN'):
        super(FractureNet, self).__init__()
        mapping_size = 128
        self.branch_net_u = Modified_MLP_Block(2, 50, 40)
        self.trunk_net_u = Modified_MLP_Block(2 * mapping_size+5, 50, 40)

        self.branch_net_s = Modified_MLP_Block(2, 50, 40)
        self.trunk_net_s = Modified_MLP_Block(2 * mapping_size+5+2, 50, 40)

        self.branch_net_p = Modified_MLP_Block(2, 50, 40)
        self.trunk_net_p = Modified_MLP_Block(2 * mapping_size+5+2, 50, 40)
        self.mode = mode
        if self.mode == 'norm_GCN':
            # 0) 基础GCN
            self.pointnet = PointGNNEncoder(in_dim=3, hidden_dim=64, out_dim=point_dim)
        elif self.mode == 'deep_GCN':
            # 1) 更深GCN
            self.pointnet = DeepGCNEncoder(in_dim=3, hidden_dim=128, out_dim=point_dim, num_layers=6)
        elif self.mode == 'GAT':
            # 2) 图注意力
            self.pointnet = GATEncoder(in_dim=3, hidden_dim=64, out_dim=point_dim, heads=4, layers=3)
        elif self.mode == 'G_UNet':
            # 3) 图UNet
            self.pointnet = GraphUNetEncoder(in_dim=3, hidden_dim=64, out_dim=point_dim, depth=4, pool_ratios=0.5)
        elif self.mode == 'EGNN':
            # 4) EGNN（需要 batch_graph.pos）
            # 若 x=[x,y,phi]，请把 Data.pos=x[:,:2]，Data.x=x[:,2:3] 再送入
            self.pointnet = EGNNEncoder(in_dim=1, coord_dim=2, hidden_dim=64, out_dim=point_dim, layers=4)
        elif self.mode == 'GIN':
            # 5) GIN + TopKPool
            self.pointnet = GINTopKEncoder(in_dim=3, hidden_dim=64, out_dim=point_dim, pool_ratio=0.8, layers=3)
        else:
            raise NotImplementedError
        self.fourier = FourierEmbedding(2, mapping_size=mapping_size)

        self.fusion_u = MLP_Block(40 + point_dim, 50, 40, 2)
        self.fusion_s = MLP_Block(40 + point_dim, 50, 40, 2)
        self.fusion_p = MLP_Block(40 + point_dim, 50, 40, 2)

        self.dim_u = 2
        self.dim_s = 1
        self.dim_p = 1

    def forward(self, B_cond, B_phase, T_data):
        """
        B_cond: [N_b, 2]    条件输入
        B_phase: [Np, 3]    裂隙点云
        T_data: [N_t, 2]    查询点
        """
        x, y = T_data[..., 0:1], T_data[..., 1:2]
        xy_embed = torch.cat([x, y, x**2, y**2, x*y], dim=-1)
        T_data = torch.cat([self.fourier(T_data), xy_embed], dim=-1)

        graph_batch = pointcloud_to_graph(B_phase, k=8, if_depart = self.mode == 'EGNN')  # 转图
        p_feat = self.pointnet(graph_batch)
        # 1阶段 --> 位移
        B_u = self.branch_net_u(B_cond)
        T_u = self.trunk_net_u(T_data)
        N_u, _ = T_u.shape
        P_u = p_feat.expand(N_u, -1)  # [N_t, point_dim]
        fusion_input = torch.cat([B_u, P_u], dim=-1)  # [N_b + N_t, fusion_dim]
        feature_u = self.fusion_u(fusion_input)  # [B, N_t, out_dim]

        B_u_split = feature_u.chunk(self.dim_u, dim=-1)
        T_u_split = T_u.chunk(self.dim_u, dim=-1)
        u_out = [torch.sum(B_u_split[i] * T_u_split[i], dim=-1, keepdim=True) for i in range(self.dim_u)]
        u_pred = torch.cat(u_out, dim=-1)

        # 2阶段 --> 应力
        trunk_input_s = torch.cat([T_data, u_pred.detach()], dim=-1)
        B_s = self.branch_net_s(B_cond)
        T_s = self.trunk_net_s(trunk_input_s)

        N_t, _ = T_s.shape
        P_s = p_feat.expand(N_t, -1)  # [N_t, point_dim]
        fusion_input = torch.cat([B_s, P_s], dim=-1)  # [N_b + N_t, fusion_dim]
        feature_s = self.fusion_s(fusion_input)  # [B, N_t, out_dim]

        B_s_split = feature_s.chunk(self.dim_s, dim=-1)
        T_s_split = T_s.chunk(self.dim_s, dim=-1)
        s_out = [torch.sum(B_s_split[i] * T_s_split[i], dim=-1, keepdim=True) for i in range(self.dim_s)]

        # 3阶段 --> 裂隙场
        trunk_input_p = torch.cat([T_data, u_pred.detach()], dim=-1)

        B_p = self.branch_net_p(B_cond)
        T_p = self.trunk_net_p(trunk_input_p)

        N_p, _ = T_p.shape
        P_p = p_feat.expand(N_p, -1)  # [N_t, point_dim]
        fusion_input = torch.cat([B_p, P_p], dim=-1)  # [N_b + N_t, fusion_dim]
        feature_p = self.fusion_p(fusion_input)  # [B, N_t, out_dim]

        B_p_split = feature_p.chunk(self.dim_p, dim=-1)
        T_p_split = T_p.chunk(self.dim_p, dim=-1)
        p_out = [torch.sum(B_p_split[i] * T_p_split[i], dim=-1, keepdim=True) for i in range(self.dim_p)]
        return u_out[0], u_out[1], s_out[0], p_out[0]

def load_crack_dataset(base_dir, mode="train", l0_list=None, step_interval=5, step_max=1200):
    """
    参数:
        base_dir (str): 数据集根目录，例如 "F:\\DeepLearningDataset\\Crack"
        mode (str): "train" 或 "test"
        l0_list (list[int]): 初始裂隙长度列表，例如 [30,35,...] 或 [20,37,...]
        step_interval (int): step 间隔，默认 5
        step_max (int): 最大 step，默认 1200
    返回:
        data_dict (dict): { l0: {step: DataFrame} }
    """
    data_dict = {}
    data_dir = os.path.join(base_dir, f"{mode.capitalize()}_data")
    for l0 in l0_list:
        l0_dir = os.path.join(data_dir, str(l0))
        if not os.path.exists(l0_dir):
            print(f"Warning: {l0_dir} 不存在，跳过")
            continue

        step_dict = {}
        for step in range(step_interval, step_max + 1, step_interval):
            file_name = f"results_step_{step:03d}.csv"
            file_path = os.path.join(l0_dir, file_name)

            if os.path.exists(file_path):
                df = pd.read_csv(file_path)
                df['phase'] = np.clip(df['phase'],0,1)
                step_dict[step] = df
            else:
                print(f"Warning: {file_path} 缺失")
        data_dict[l0] = step_dict
    return data_dict

class FractureDataset(Dataset):
    def __init__(self, samples, norm_stats=None, mode="train"):
        self.samples = samples
        self.mode = mode

        if norm_stats is None and mode == "train":
            B_cond_all = np.concatenate([s["B_cond"][0] for s in samples], axis=0)
            T_all = np.concatenate([s["T_data"] for s in samples], axis=0)
            U_all = np.concatenate([s["U_data"] for s in samples], axis=0)
            S_all = np.concatenate([s["S_data"] for s in samples], axis=0)

            self.norm_stats = {
                "B_mean": B_cond_all.mean(0), "B_std": B_cond_all.std(0) + 1e-8,
                "T_mean": T_all.mean(0), "T_std": T_all.std(0) + 1e-8,
                "U_mean": U_all.mean(0), "U_std": U_all.std(0) + 1e-8,
                "S_mean": S_all.mean(0), "S_std": S_all.std(0) + 1e-8,
            }
        else:
            self.norm_stats = norm_stats

        # 标准化
        for s in self.samples:
            s["B_cond"] = (s["B_cond"] - self.norm_stats["B_mean"]) / self.norm_stats["B_std"]
            s["T_data"] = (s["T_data"] - self.norm_stats["T_mean"]) / self.norm_stats["T_std"]
            s["U_data"] = (s["U_data"] - self.norm_stats["U_mean"]) / self.norm_stats["U_std"]
            s["S_data"] = (s["S_data"] - self.norm_stats["S_mean"]) / self.norm_stats["S_std"]

    def __len__(self):
        return len(self.samples)

    def __getitem__(self, field_idx):
        s = self.samples[field_idx]
        return (
            torch.tensor(s["B_cond"], dtype=torch.float32),
            torch.tensor(s["B_phase"],dtype=torch.float32),
            torch.tensor(s["T_data"], dtype=torch.float32),
            torch.tensor(s["U_data"], dtype=torch.float32),
            torch.tensor(s["S_data"], dtype=torch.float32),
            torch.tensor(s["phase"],  dtype=torch.float32),
        )

def build_dataset_from_dict(data_dict):
    samples = []
    for l0, steps in data_dict.items():
        step_list = sorted(steps.keys())
        for i in range(1, len(step_list)):
            step_prev = step_list[i-1]
            step_now = step_list[i]
            df_prev = steps[step_prev]
            df_now = steps[step_now]

            # 对应点匹配 (假设网格一致)
            x = df_now["x"].values
            y = df_now["y"].values
            x_prev = df_prev["x"].values
            y_prev = df_prev["y"].values
            u = df_now["u"].values
            v = df_now["v"].values
            s_vm = df_now["sigma_vm"].values
            phase_now = df_now["phase"].values
            phase_prev = df_prev["phase"].values
            B_cond = np.array([l0, step_now], dtype=np.float32)
            B_cond = np.tile(B_cond, (len(x), 1))
            sample = {
                "B_cond": B_cond,
                "B_phase": np.stack([x_prev, y_prev, phase_prev], axis=1).reshape(-1, 3),      # (l_{t-1}, 3)
                "T_data": np.stack([x, y], axis=1),       # (N, 2)
                "U_data": np.stack([u, v], axis=1),       # (N, 2)
                "S_data": s_vm.reshape(-1, 1),            # (N, 1)
                "phase": phase_now.reshape(-1, 1),       # (l_t, 1)
            }
            samples.append(sample)
    return samples

def create_dataloaders(train_data, test_data):
    train_samples = build_dataset_from_dict(train_data)
    test_samples  = build_dataset_from_dict(test_data)

    train_dataset = FractureDataset(train_samples, norm_stats=None, mode="train")
    norm_stats = train_dataset.norm_stats

    test_dataset = FractureDataset(test_samples, norm_stats=norm_stats, mode="test")

    return train_dataset, test_dataset, norm_stats

class PINN_Vibrate:
    def __init__(self, train_model, learning_rate = 0.001, step = 200, gamma = 0.95):
        self.device = torch.device("cuda" if torch.cuda.is_available() else "cpu")
        print(self.device)
        self.model = train_model.to(self.device)
        self.criterion = nn.MSELoss()
        self.optimizer = torch.optim.Adam(self.model.parameters(), lr=learning_rate)
        self.scheduler = torch.optim.lr_scheduler.StepLR(self.optimizer, step_size=step, gamma=gamma)
        self.Losses = []
        self.Lambda = []
        self.file_name = r"F:\Pycharm\Pycharm_Files\Pytorch\DeepLearning\Crack\Crack2.pkl"
        self.train_data, self.test_data, self.train_dataset, self.test_dataset, self.norm_stats = self.load_train_set()

    def load_model(self):
        try:
            self.model.load_state_dict(torch.load(self.file_name, weights_only=True))
            print('model loaded')
        except Exception as e:
            print(f'Error with loading model: {e}')
        
    def u_function(self, B_cond, B_phase, T_data):
        u, v, s, p = self.model(B_cond, B_phase, T_data)
        return u, v, s, p
        
    def train(self, train_epochs):
        self.Losses.append(['total loss', 'U loss', 'S-VM loss', 'Phase loss'])
        print('training started')
        start_time = datetime.datetime.now()
        for epoch in range(train_epochs):
            item_loss = 0.
            item_dx_loss = 0.
            item_svm_loss = 0.
            item_phase_loss = 0.
            random_indices = np.random.permutation(len(self.train_dataset))
            for field_idx in random_indices:
                B_cond, B_phase, T_data, U_data, S_data, phase = self.train_dataset[field_idx]
                phase_idx = self.sampling(torch.hstack([T_data, phase]), num_samples=10000)
                B_cond = B_cond[phase_idx]
                T_data = T_data[phase_idx]
                U_data = U_data[phase_idx]
                S_data = S_data[phase_idx]
                phase  = phase[phase_idx]

                B_cond, B_phase = B_cond.to(self.device), B_phase.to(self.device)
                T_data, U_data = T_data.to(self.device).requires_grad_(True), U_data.to(self.device)
                S_data, phase = S_data.to(self.device), phase.to(self.device)
                self.optimizer.zero_grad()

                u_pre, v_pre, s_pre, p_pre = self.u_function(B_cond, B_phase, T_data)
                u_ex = U_data[:,0:1]
                v_ex = U_data[:,1:2]
                s_ex = S_data[:,0:1]
                p_ex = phase[:,0:1]
                u_loss, v_loss = self.criterion(u_pre, u_ex), self.criterion(v_pre, v_ex)
                svm_loss, phase_loss = self.criterion(s_pre, s_ex), self.criterion(p_pre, p_ex)

                loss_displace = u_loss + v_loss
                loss = loss_displace + svm_loss + phase_loss
                loss.backward()
                self.optimizer.step()
                item_loss += loss.item()
                item_dx_loss += loss_displace.item()
                item_svm_loss += svm_loss.item()
                item_phase_loss += phase_loss.item()

            self.Losses.append([
                item_loss/len(self.train_dataset),
                item_dx_loss/len(self.train_dataset),
                item_svm_loss/len(self.train_dataset),
                item_phase_loss/len(self.train_dataset),
            ])
            self.scheduler.step()
            if epoch % 10 == 0 or epoch == train_epochs - 1:
                print(f"[Epoch {epoch+1}/{train_epochs}] [loss: {item_loss/len(self.train_dataset):.8f}] "
                      f"[loss_data: {item_dx_loss/len(self.train_dataset):.8f}] "
                      f"[loss_svm: {item_svm_loss/len(self.train_dataset):.8f}] "
                      f"[loss_phase: {item_phase_loss/len(self.train_dataset):.8f}]]")
                torch.save(self.model.state_dict(), self.file_name)
        torch.save(self.model.state_dict(), self.file_name)
        print("Current learning rate:", self.optimizer.param_groups[0]['lr'])
        print("Training Time:", (datetime.datetime.now() - start_time).total_seconds() / 3600, "h")

    def sampling(self, points, num_samples): # 分区抽样
        ratio = 0.7
        phase_threshold = 0.5
        N = points.shape[0]
        phases = points[:, 2]

        crack_mask = phases > phase_threshold
        crack_idx = torch.nonzero(crack_mask, as_tuple=True)[0]
        background_idx = torch.nonzero(~crack_mask, as_tuple=True)[0]

        num_crack = int(num_samples * ratio)
        num_background = num_samples - num_crack

        # 裂隙区采样
        if len(crack_idx) > 0:
            crack_sampled = crack_idx[torch.randint(0, len(crack_idx), (min(num_crack, len(crack_idx)),))]
        else:
            crack_sampled = torch.tensor([], dtype=torch.long, device=points.device)

        # 背景区采样
        if len(background_idx) > 0:
            background_sampled = background_idx[torch.randint(0, len(background_idx), (min(num_background, len(background_idx)),))]
        else:
            background_sampled = torch.tensor([], dtype=torch.long, device=points.device)

        idx = torch.cat([crack_sampled, background_sampled])

        if idx.numel() < num_samples:
            extra_idx = torch.randint(0, N, (num_samples - idx.numel(),), device=points.device)
            idx = torch.cat([idx, extra_idx])
        return idx

    def plot_loss(self):
        if not self.Losses or len(self.Losses) <= 1:

        plt.title('log(loss)')
        temp = np.array(self.Losses[1:])

        plt.yscale('log')
        plt.legend()
        plt.show()

    def compute_samplewise_error(self, dataset, u_function, batch_size=10000):
        strain_u_errors = []
        strain_v_errors = []
        stress_errors = []
        phase_errors = []
        criterion = nn.MSELoss(reduction='none')
        with (torch.no_grad()):
            for field_idx in range(len(dataset)):
                B_cond, B_phase, T_data, U_data, S_data, phase = dataset[field_idx]
                N = B_cond.shape[0]
                field_u_err = []
                field_v_err = []
                field_s_err = []
                field_p_err = []
                for start in range(0, N, batch_size):
                    end = min(start + batch_size, N)
                    B_cond_b = B_cond[start:end].to(self.device)
                    B_phase_b = B_phase.to(self.device)
                    T_data_b = T_data[start:end].to(self.device)
                    U_data_b = U_data[start:end].to(self.device)
                    S_data_b = S_data[start:end].to(self.device)
                    phase_b  = phase[start:end].to(self.device)
                    u_ex = U_data_b[:, 0:1]
                    v_ex = U_data_b[:, 1:2]
                    svm_ex = S_data_b[:,0:1]
                    phase_ex = phase_b[:,0:1]

                    u_pre, v_pre, svm_pre, phase_pre = u_function(B_cond_b, B_phase_b, T_data_b)

                    field_u_err.append(criterion(u_pre, u_ex).detach().cpu())
                    field_v_err.append(criterion(v_pre, v_ex).detach().cpu())
                    field_s_err.append(criterion(svm_pre, svm_ex).detach().cpu())
                    field_p_err.append(criterion(phase_pre, phase_ex).detach().cpu())

            field_u_err_tensor = torch.cat(field_u_err, dim=0)
            field_v_err_tensor = torch.cat(field_v_err, dim=0)
            field_s_err_tensor = torch.cat(field_s_err, dim=0)
            field_p_err_tensor = torch.cat(field_p_err, dim=0)

            strain_u_errors.append(torch.mean(field_u_err_tensor).item())
            strain_v_errors.append(torch.mean(field_v_err_tensor).item())
            stress_errors.append(torch.mean(field_s_err_tensor).item())
            phase_errors.append(torch.mean(field_p_err_tensor).item())
        return strain_u_errors, strain_v_errors, stress_errors, phase_errors

    def get_predict(self, B_cond, B_phase, T_data):
        with torch.no_grad():
            u_pre, v_pre, svm_pre, phase_pre = self.u_function(B_cond, B_phase, T_data)
            U_pre = torch.cat([u_pre.reshape(-1,1), v_pre.reshape(-1,1)], dim=1).cpu().detach().numpy()
            u_np = U_pre[:,0:1].reshape(-1,1) * self.norm_stats['U_std'][0] + self.norm_stats['U_mean'][0]
            v_np = U_pre[:,1:2].reshape(-1,1) * self.norm_stats['U_std'][1] + self.norm_stats['U_mean'][1]
            svm_np = (svm_pre.cpu().detach().numpy().reshape(-1,1)) * self.norm_stats['S_std'] + self.norm_stats['S_mean']
            phase_np = phase_pre.cpu().detach().numpy().reshape(-1,1)
        return u_np, v_np, svm_np, phase_np

    def get_exact(self, U_data, S_data, phase):
        U_ex = U_data.cpu().detach().numpy()
        u_ex = U_ex[:,0:1].reshape(-1,1) * self.norm_stats['U_std'][0] + self.norm_stats['U_mean'][0]
        v_ex = U_ex[:,1:2].reshape(-1,1) * self.norm_stats['U_std'][1] + self.norm_stats['U_mean'][1]
        svm_ex = S_data[:,0:1].cpu().detach().numpy().reshape(-1,1) * self.norm_stats['S_std'] + self.norm_stats['S_mean']
        phase = phase.cpu().detach().numpy().reshape(-1,1)
        return u_ex, v_ex, svm_ex, phase

    def plot_strain(self, num=0, mode='test'):
        B_cond, B_phase, T_data, U_data, S_data, phase = self.get_test_data(num, mode=mode, if_random=True)
        B_cond_ = B_cond.cpu().detach().numpy() * self.norm_stats['B_std'] + self.norm_stats['B_mean']
        l0, step = B_cond_[0][0], B_cond_[0][1]
        print(f"Param: l0 = {l0} step = {step}")

        B_cond, B_phase, T_data = B_cond.to(self.device), B_phase.to(self.device), T_data.to(self.device)
        U_data, S_data = U_data.to(self.device), S_data.to(self.device)

        u_pre, v_pre, _, _ = self.get_predict(B_cond, B_phase, T_data)
        u_ex, v_ex, _, _ = self.get_exact(U_data, S_data, phase)

        u_pre, v_pre = u_pre.flatten(), v_pre.flatten()
        u_ex, v_ex = u_ex.flatten(), v_ex.flatten()

        X_np = T_data.cpu().detach().numpy() * self.norm_stats['T_std'] + self.norm_stats['T_mean']
        x_np = X_np[:,0:1].reshape(-1,1).flatten()
        y_np = X_np[:,1:2].reshape(-1,1).flatten()

        X_pre = (x_np + u_pre)
        Y_pre = (y_np + v_pre)

        X_ex = (x_np + u_ex)
        Y_ex = (y_np + v_ex)

        u_err = np.abs(u_ex - u_pre)
        v_err = np.abs(v_ex - v_pre)

        print(f'RMSE U = {np.linalg.norm(u_err)/np.linalg.norm(u_ex)} RMSE V = {np.linalg.norm(v_err)/np.linalg.norm(v_ex)}')
        print(f'MAE U = {np.mean(np.abs(u_err))} MAE V = {np.mean(np.abs(v_err))}')
        plt.figure(figsize=(18,9))
        for i, temp in enumerate([[X_pre,Y_pre,u_pre,'U Pre'],[X_ex,Y_ex,u_ex,'U Exact'],[X_pre,Y_pre,u_err,'U Error'],
                                  [X_pre,Y_pre,v_pre,'V Pre'],[X_ex,Y_ex,v_ex,'V Exact'],[X_pre,Y_pre,v_err,'V Error']]):
            plt.subplot(2,3,i+1)
            tri = plt.tricontourf(temp[0], temp[1], temp[2], levels=100, cmap='bwr')
            plt.colorbar(tri)
            plt.xlabel('x')
            plt.ylabel('y')
            plt.title(temp[3])
            plt.tight_layout()
        plt.show()

        fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(12, 5))

        for i, x_target in enumerate([0.5, 0.75]):
            tol = 1e-4
            idx = np.where(np.abs(x_np - x_target) < tol)[0]
            if len(idx) == 0:
                print(f"No points found near x = {x_target} mm")
                continue

            y_slice = y_np[idx]
            u_pre_slice = u_pre[idx]
            u_ex_slice = u_ex[idx]
            v_pre_slice = v_pre[idx]
            v_ex_slice = v_ex[idx]

            sort_idx = np.argsort(y_slice)

            axes[i].plot(y_slice[sort_idx], u_pre_slice[sort_idx], 'r--', label='u_pred')
            axes[i].plot(y_slice[sort_idx], u_ex_slice[sort_idx], 'r-', label='u_exact')
            axes[i].plot(y_slice[sort_idx], v_pre_slice[sort_idx], 'b--', label='v_pred')
            axes[i].plot(y_slice[sort_idx], v_ex_slice[sort_idx], 'b-', label='v_exact')

            axes[i].set_title(f'X = {x_target:.4f} mm')
            axes[i].set_xlabel('y [mm]')
            axes[i].set_ylabel('Displacement')
            axes[i].legend()
            axes[i].grid(True)

        plt.tight_layout()
        plt.show()

    def get_test_data(self, number=0, mode='test', if_random=False, random_seed=42):
        if mode == 'test':
            dataset = self.test_dataset
        elif mode == 'train':
            dataset = self.train_dataset
        else:
            dataset = self.test_dataset
        if if_random:
            rng = list(range(len(dataset)))
            random.Random(random_seed).shuffle(rng)
            number = rng[number % len(dataset)]
        B_cond, B_phase, T_data, U_data, S_data, phase = dataset[number]
        return B_cond, B_phase, T_data, U_data, S_data, phase
        
    def load_train_set(self):
        base_dir = r"F:\DeepLearningDataset\Crack"
        train_l0 = [30, 35, 40, 45, 50, 55, 60]
        train_data = load_crack_dataset(base_dir, mode="train", l0_list=train_l0, step_interval=5)

        test_l0 = [20, 37, 53, 70]
        test_data = load_crack_dataset(base_dir, mode="test", l0_list=test_l0, step_interval=5)
        train_dataset, test_dataset, norm_stats = create_dataloaders(train_data, test_data)
        return train_data, test_data, train_dataset, test_dataset, norm_stats
